'''馬克斯·艾米利安·維斯塔潘'''（{{lang-nl|Max Emilian Verstappen}}，{{bd|1997年|9月30日}}），是[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]車手，現時效力[[紅牛車隊|紅牛車隊]]。維斯塔潘是世界一级方程式锦标赛中最年轻的领跑车手、最年轻的单圈最快车手、最年轻的得分车手、最年輕的大滿貫冠軍車手和最年轻的分站冠军得主。他在[[2021年世界一级方程式锦标赛|2021年世界一级方程式锦标赛]]擊敗[[路易斯·咸美頓|路易斯·咸美頓]]贏得首座[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|一級方程式賽車世界冠軍]]。<ref name="世界冠軍">{{Cite web|title=Max Verstappen beats Lewis Hamilton to F1 world title on last lap in Abu Dhabi|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2021/dec/12/f1-max-verstappen-wins-abu-dhabi-gp-lewis-hamilton|publisher=The Guardian|date=2021-12-12|access-date=2021-12-12|archive-date=2021-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221110645/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2021/dec/12/f1-max-verstappen-wins-abu-dhabi-gp-lewis-hamilton|dead-url=no}}</ref>

維斯塔潘在2014年參加[[國際汽車聯盟歐洲三級方程式賽車錦標賽|國際汽車聯盟歐洲三級方程式賽車錦標賽]]，並在[[2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2015年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]加入[[紅牛二隊|紅牛二隊]]，以17岁166天的年龄成为一级方程式锦标赛中最年轻的车手。他在[[红牛二队|红牛二队]]完成[[2015年世界一级方程式锦标赛|2015赛季]]和[[2016年世界一级方程式锦标赛|2016赛季]]最初四场比赛后，他晋升至[[红牛车队|红牛车队]]。随后在[[2016年西班牙大獎賽|2016年西班牙大獎賽]]上，18岁的維斯塔潘夺得个人生涯首个分站冠军，成為歷年來最年輕分站冠軍得主和首位奪冠的荷蘭籍车手。<ref name="Spanish Grand Prix race report">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/may/15/f1-spanish-gp-live-lewis-hamilton-nico-rosberg|title=Max Verstappen wins Spanish GP after Lewis Hamilton and Nico Rosberg crash – as it happened|work=www.bbc.co.uk|date=15 May 2016|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515143832/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/live/2016/may/15/f1-spanish-gp-live-lewis-hamilton-nico-rosberg|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==家庭和個人生活==
馬克斯出生於賽車世家。他的父親是前[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]車手[[喬斯·維斯塔潘|喬斯·維斯塔潘]]，母親蘇菲·庫彭（Sophie Kumpen）是一位成功的比利時籍前卡丁車手。他的外祖父{{le|保羅·庫彭|Paul Kumpen}}是前GT耐力賽車手<ref>{{cite web|title=Paul Kumpen|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/driver/results/Paul-Kumpen-B.html|work=Racing Sportscars|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805060557/http://www.racingsportscars.com/driver/results/Paul-Kumpen-B.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，舅舅{{le|安東尼·庫彭|Anthony Kumpen}}則是[[FIA_GT錦標賽|FIA GT錦標賽]]與[[利曼24小時耐力賽|利曼24小時耐力賽]]車手。

維斯塔潘目前與巴西籍三屆[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]世界冠軍[[尼爾遜·畢奇|尼爾遜·畢奇]]的女兒{{link-en|凱莉·皮奎特|Kelly Piquet}}交往中。<ref>{{cite web|title=Max Verstappen's secret weapon! Driver, 24, has one over on rival Lewis Hamilton thanks to his supportive model girlfriend Kelly, 33, who's the daughter of Nelson Piquet|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-10284233/Max-Verstappens-secret-weapon-Driver-24-supportive-model-girlfriend-Kelly-33.html|publisher=Daily Mail|date=2021-12-07|access-date=2021-12-11|archive-date=2022-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220201004822/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-10284233/Max-Verstappens-secret-weapon-Driver-24-supportive-model-girlfriend-Kelly-33.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

比利時籍三屆[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英格兰足球超级联赛]]冠軍足球員[[凯文·德布劳内|凯文·德布劳内]]是維斯塔潘的支持者。<ref>{{cite web|title=Man City star Kevin De Bruyne sends Max Verstappen message ahead of Lewis Hamilton finale|url=https://www.express.co.uk/sport/f1-autosport/1534577/Man-City-Kevin-De-Bruyne-Max-Verstappen-Lewis-Hamilton-Premier-League-F1-news|publisher=Daily Express|date=2021-12-11|access-date=2021-12-11|archive-date=2021-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211211145921/https://www.express.co.uk/sport/f1-autosport/1534577/Man-City-Kevin-De-Bruyne-Max-Verstappen-Lewis-Hamilton-Premier-League-F1-news|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
===卡丁車===
維斯塔潘自4歲半時開始駕駛[[卡丁車|卡丁車]]。他參加了家鄉[[林堡省_(荷蘭)|林堡省]]的迷你青少年錦標賽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Limburgs Kart Championship – Mini-Junior 2005|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/limburgs-kart-championship---mini-junior/2005/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154144/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/limburgs-kart-championship---mini-junior/2005/|dead-url=no}}</ref>維斯塔潘在2006年晉升至{{le|羅泰克斯Max|Rotax Max}}卡丁車挑戰賽MiniMax級別，並贏得了比利時錦標賽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rotax Max Challenge Belgium Minimax 2006|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/rotax-max-challenge-belgium-minimax/2006/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522155445/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/rotax-max-challenge-belgium-minimax/2006/|dead-url=no}}</ref>接著他在2007年贏得了荷蘭Minimax錦標賽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rotax Max Challenge Belgium Minimax 2007|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/dutch-championship-rotax-max-minimax/2007/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154158/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/dutch-championship-rotax-max-minimax/2007/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後他駕駛CRG卡丁車，贏得了荷蘭與比利時Minimax錦標賽，以及比利時見習生錦標賽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Belgian Championship – Cadet 2008|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/belgian-championship---cadet/2008/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154236/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/belgian-championship---cadet/2008/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rotax Max Challenge Belgium Minimax 2008|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/rotax-max-challenge-belgium-minimax/2008/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154239/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/rotax-max-challenge-belgium-minimax/2008/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

維斯塔潘在2009年加入了使用CRG卡丁車的佩克斯車隊（Team Pex Racing），並獲得[[法蘭德斯|法蘭德斯]]Minimax錦標賽及比利時KF5錦標賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=Belgian Championship – KF5 2009|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/belgian-championship---kf5/2009/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154217/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/belgian-championship---kf5/2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=VAS Championship – Rotax Minimax 2009|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/vas-championship---rotax-minimax/2009/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154235/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/vas-championship---rotax-minimax/2009/|dead-url=no}}</ref>接著維斯塔潘在2010年被CRG簽下，晉升至國際卡丁車賽，為他們的廠隊出戰世界及歐洲錦標賽。之後他在KF3世界盃獲得了亞軍，僅落後經驗較豐富的[[亞歷山大·艾邦|亞歷山大·艾邦]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=CIK-FIA World Cup – KF3 2010|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/world-cup---kf3/2010/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154227/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/world-cup---kf3/2010/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他在之後的WSK歐洲系列賽便打敗了艾邦，贏得冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=WSK World Series – KF3 2010|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/wsk-euro-series---kf3/2010/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2020-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602031103/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/wsk-euro-series---kf3/2010/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

維斯塔潘在2011年駕駛帕里拉（Parilla）引擎的CRG卡丁車，再度贏得WSK歐洲系列賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=WSK Euro Series – KF3 2011|url=http://www.driverdb.com/standings/6069-2011/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2020-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602030647/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/wsk-euro-series---kf3/2011/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2012年加入了[[Intrepid卡丁車|Intrepid]]車手計畫，出賽KF2與KZ2兩個級別。他在KF2級別中打敗了費利斯·蒂埃內（Felice Tiene），贏得WSK大師系列賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=WSK Master Series – KF2 2012|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/wsk-master-series---kf2/2012/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154309/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/wsk-master-series---kf2/2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他也曾在南加爾達冬季盃的KF2級別打敗{{le|丹尼斯·奧爾森|Dennis Olsen (racing driver)}}及{{le|安東尼奧·富奧科|Antonio Fuoco}}獲得冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=17° Winter Cup – KF2 2012|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/south-garda-winter-cup---kf2/2012/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154314/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/south-garda-winter-cup---kf2/2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年底，維斯塔潘宣布他將會離開Intrepid。在短暫地駕駛CRG製造的[[亞歷士·辛尼迪|辛尼迪]]卡丁車後，維斯塔潘再度重返CRG廠隊。<ref>{{cite web|title=Max rijdt rest van seizoen op CRG kart met TM motor|url=http://www.verstappen.nl/nieuws/2012/08/8038.html|work=Verstappen Info Page|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2020-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313160617/https://www.verstappen.nl/nieuws/2012/08/8038.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他參加了SKUSA SuperNationals卡丁車大賽的KZ2級別，駕駛著一輛CRG，最終名列第21位。<ref>{{cite web|title=SKUSA SuperNationals XVI – KZ2 2012|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/skusa-supernationals---kz2/2012/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154319/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/skusa-supernationals---kz2/2012/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之後，維斯塔潘在2013年贏得了歐洲KF與KZ錦標賽的冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=CIK-FIA European Championship KF 2013|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/european-championship---kf2/2013/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154321/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/european-championship---kf2/2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=CIK-FIA European Championship - KZ 2013|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/european-championship-kz/2013/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2021-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210522154316/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/european-championship-kz/2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>接著他在15歲時，於[[法國|法國]][[阿列河畔瓦雷讷|阿列河畔瓦雷讷]]的2013年世界KZ錦標賽中，贏得了卡丁車最高級別——KZ1級別的冠軍。<ref>{{cite web|title=CIK-FIA World KZ Championship 2013|url=https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/world-championship-kz/2013/|work=DriverDB.com|accessdate=2014-01-27|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327160550/https://www.driverdb.com/championships/standings/world-championship-kz/2013/|dead-url=no}}<